### Ask POE
POST http://localhost:3000/assistant HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "query": "Hello, whats Your name?",
    "type": "query",
    "category": "message",
    "chatParams": {
        "model": "gpt-3.5-turbo"
    },
    "context": "Just answer in English and tell me something about Yourself"
}


